  <trk>
    <name>Engelstock circular route</name>
    <desc><![CDATA[The rotating gondola takes you directly to the Engelstock circular route, which leads along an easy terrain with a fantastic panorama. From the Mostelberg mountain station, you follow a wide path literally around the Engelstock. Almost throughout the entire route, you have a unique view of the southern Alps or the Mythen massif and the Muotathal mountain world.]]></desc>
    <type>themeTrail</type>
